The aim of a pebble script should be to find the lowest common
denominators involved in daily linux command usage into a script
pebble with the most used arguments

Pebble scripts are housed in beds/servers.

The default pebbles for the different types of beds can be found in ../beds/*
pebble spec:
 - must interpret stdin, stderr, stdout and exit with a code
 - must be self maintainable
 - must be serially configurable
